"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:11.3.1.8\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">11.3.1.8</span> 標題：欣（hin）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： הִין</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： hin)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:40\">EXO 29:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:40\">EXO 29:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:24\">EXO 30:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:36\">LEV 19:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:13\">LEV 23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:4\">NUM 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:5\">NUM 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:6\">NUM 15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:7\">NUM 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:9\">NUM 15:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:10\">NUM 15:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:5\">NUM 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:7\">NUM 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:14\">NUM 28:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:14\">NUM 28:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:14\">NUM 28:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:11\">EZK 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:24\">EZK 45:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:5\">EZK 46:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:7\">EZK 46:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:11\">EZK 46:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:14\">EZK 46:14</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <em>Hin</em> （欣）是一種液量，用來衡量祭物裡面調和的酒和油，以及聖膏裡面調和的油。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:36\">LEV 19:36</a> ：參上文<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">11.3.1.3 伊法（ephah）&lt;REALIA:11.3.1.3&gt;</a> 關於伊法的註解。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:11\">EZK 4:11</a> ：關於以西結在表演耶路撒冷被圍的街頭劇時每天喝的水量，各譯本有不同的譯法，如「三分之二夸脫」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"God&#x27;s Word Translation\">GW</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直譯）、「兩杯」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直譯）、「兩大杯」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 直譯）等。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
